    "description": "<br><br>《卡牌法师》是一款动作类 roguelite 游戏，将近战战斗与基于卡牌的施法完美融合在了一起，挑战您快速思考和施法的能力。穿行在支离破碎的国度中，与魔法卡牌决斗，对抗冰冷的钢铁洪流。单枪匹马或与好友组队，在征服奥术锦标赛的途中与奇幻野兽和敌对法师战斗。<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053880/extras/62a15839b34dd1ab6fa3f2104048c679.poster.avif?t=1723041048\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053880/extras/62a15839b34dd1ab6fa3f2104048c679.webm?t=1723041048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053880/extras/62a15839b34dd1ab6fa3f2104048c679.mp4?t=1723041048\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >构建奥术牌组</h2> 每张卡牌在打出时都会施放一个法术，譬如炽热火球术、变羊诅咒、复活或召唤魔法。<br> 尝试使用卡牌组合构建一个势不可挡的牌组，碾碎您在旅途中遇到的任何敌人。<br> 为小丑牌牌配备突破规则的效果，让您的法术千变万化，并利用从杀死高大 Boss 或从行游商人那里购买的独特卡牌来创建强大的组合。<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053880/extras/8796d8eb1903e4faaf9059c51d43f4e3.poster.avif?t=1723041048\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053880/extras/8796d8eb1903e4faaf9059c51d43f4e3.webm?t=1723041048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053880/extras/8796d8eb1903e4faaf9059c51d43f4e3.mp4?t=1723041048\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >刀剑法术混战</h2> 结合法法术攻击和近战攻击，掌握魔法战斗之道。将您的牌组用作武器，施放法术从远处消灭敌人，然后利用刀剑近距离斩杀敌人。保持灵活的机动性，在敌人的猛攻和环境危害中生存下来，这些对您的反应能力、战术思维和牌组构建技能提出了考验。<br> 所有战斗都发生在精心手绘的环境中，伴随着程序生成的威胁，穿越被魔法大灾变摧毁的土地。<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053880/extras/fd7077e5f381fabd0ef2ab121cd1d1b6.poster.avif?t=1723041048\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053880/extras/fd7077e5f381fabd0ef2ab121cd1d1b6.webm?t=1723041048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053880/extras/fd7077e5f381fabd0ef2ab121cd1d1b6.mp4?t=1723041048\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >奥术锦标赛</h2> 您的旅程将在奥术锦标赛中达到高潮，您收集的卡牌和来之不易的技能将面临终极考验，从而证明您对魔法和战斗的精通程度。<br> 如果您不幸失败了，那么失败将助您获得更加强大的力量。<br> 每次挑战都会解锁新卡牌和卡牌法师，逐渐丰富您的魔法收藏，结合更多效果，从而获得更多惊人与千变万化的的协同效果。<br><br>",
